{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Tools/notion-글꼴바꾸기/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Noah's Dev Log","author":"[SeungHyun]","siteUrl":"https://noah0316.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"noah0316/noah0316.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"noah0316"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4fb5e97d-2ea7-5024-819a-0a9535adf5a5","excerpt":"여러분!! 안녕하세요:) 29기 아갈이 홍승현입니다🤓 오늘은 노션을 좀 더 개성있게 사용하는 법을 들고와봤습니다~~!! 다들 재밌게봐주세요 👀 Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.00.56 AM.png 우리가 그동안 썼던 노션은 글씨체가 한정되어있었는데요, 그나마 바꿀 수 있는 옵션은 Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.01.38 AM.png 글씨체의 style을 Serif 혹은 Mono…","html":"<p>여러분!! 안녕하세요:)</p>\n<p>29기 아갈이 홍승현입니다🤓</p>\n<p>오늘은 노션을 좀 더 개성있게 사용하는 법을 들고와봤습니다~~!! 다들 재밌게봐주세요 👀</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/3171ae8a-bee9-4ff0-9f52-c0ac3269b2e0/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.00.56_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.00.56 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>우리가 그동안 썼던 노션은 글씨체가 한정되어있었는데요, 그나마 바꿀 수 있는 옵션은</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/bc0efb49-c1be-43fb-9c5c-b11072c99651/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.01.38_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.01.38 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>글씨체의 style을 Serif 혹은 Mono로 바꾸는 것 뿐이었습니다🥲</p>\n<p>노션 너무나 훌륭한 툴이지만 개성넘치는 아요분들의 취향을 담기에는 2퍼센트 모자란 너낌…</p>\n<p>보기 좋은 떡이 먹기도 좋다고(?) 이왕 쓰는거 조금 더 예쁘게, 내 입맛에 맞게 사용할 방법은 없을까요?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://noticon-static.tammolo.com/dgggcrkxq/image/upload/v1567593192/noticon/za5oft8gpi5yabrlvgfp.gif\" alt=\"https://noticon-static.tammolo.com/dgggcrkxq/image/upload/v1567593192/noticon/za5oft8gpi5yabrlvgfp.gif\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/a2afd607-eea5-4992-9548-a6f3d9e2eb85/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.35.37_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.35.37 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>이렇게 폰트도 바꿔보고,</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/30aeeba7-9074-4328-8511-564dad5c2cca/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.46.41_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.46.41 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>테마도 바꿔볼 순 없을까요??</p>\n<p>notion-enhancer를 이용하면 그 모자란 2퍼센트 채울 수 있는데요!!</p>\n<p>그 2퍼센트 채우고 싶으신 분들을 위해 가져와봤습니다 👏👏👏</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/notion-enhancer/notion-enhancer\">GitHub - notion-enhancer/notion-enhancer: an enhancer/customiser for the all-in-one productivity workspace notion.so as an app</a></p>\n<p>먼저 이 링크에 접속해주세요!! (Mac 기준으로 가이드하겠습니다 ✋ <del>맥 최고</del>)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/6e742dcd-0075-4924-99cf-3e88ebecf7d8/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.13.29_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.13.29 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>여기서 밑으로 스크롤 쭈욱~~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/5681bd02-20b2-49ad-8c69-d45eb3068eb3/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.14.04_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.14.04 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>여기를 클릭해주세요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/861efd13-1409-4621-813c-098ce946ebdf/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.14.44_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.14.44 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>또 밑으로~~스크롤해주시면</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/667011eb-aa1e-425d-a945-94effd7d6dee/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.15.07_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.15.07 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>이 친구를 클릭해주세요!!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/afed10a2-9d24-4f75-aab8-6557f33139d4/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.15.44_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.15.44 AM.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/72bee8d5-0949-4dc8-bcab-0c514bc343fa/unnamed.gif\" alt=\"unnamed.gif\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"다운-중\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EC%9A%B4-%EC%A4%91\" aria-label=\"다운 중 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>다운 중…</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/17d0426d-8cea-4406-b800-dfcc34321236/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.17.53_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.17.53 AM.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/08889f52-00bd-498c-838d-0fb1d4239794/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.18.03_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.18.03 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>이 친구를 옮겨주세요!! Applications로 옮겨주세요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/6794ee6a-b9db-4649-9d31-9d8cb928e158/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.20.34_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.20.34 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>이제 Notion Enhanced라는 어플이 깔렸습니다!!</p>\n<p>이제 사용하시던 Notion을 종료해주세요!!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/2aa1c860-96a6-4794-9f41-7f5704d8d18b/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.21.45_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.21.45 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>꾸욱…</p>\n<p>고생했다…</p>\n<p>Notion Enhanced라는 어플은 Notion이라는 어플을 우리가 이용하기 쉽게 한번 더 감싼 어플이기때문에 우리는 이제 Notion대신에 Notion Enhanced라는 어플을 이용해 Notion을 사용할 거 예요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/08ff16ce-a39d-4701-a843-1017eebc8a77/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.23.05_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.23.05 AM.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"이제-notion-enhanced-어플에-들어가주세요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%9C-notion-enhanced-%EC%96%B4%ED%94%8C%EC%97%90-%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%84%B8%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"이제 notion enhanced 어플에 들어가주세요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이제 Notion Enhanced 어플에 들어가주세요!!</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/85d8e811-c26e-4f3a-8789-baccdbb8857f/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.24.23_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.24.23 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>음?? 바뀐게 없는데 (<del>이거 사기꾼 아니야??</del>)</p>\n<p>하하하하</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/b6b02746-0eeb-451d-9ecc-5887adb4ccfa/2mTP5frDW.jpeg\" alt=\"2mTP5frDW.jpeg\"></p>\n<p>아닙니다 여러분 ㅎㅎㅎ</p>\n<p>이제 가장 중요한 설정인데요, 이 기능을 통해 이제 Notion을 ‘내 취향’에 맞게 설정이 가능합니다!!</p>\n<p>기억하세요!! 단축키(<del>세미나때 팟장님 따라한거 절대 아님</del>)</p>\n<p>option키와 E 키를 함께 눌러주세요!!</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">option + E</code> 키를 함께 누르면 설정창이 뜨는데요,</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/6e6da0ae-c947-4a98-9c91-a90d6bd9a121/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.30.03_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.30.03 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>가장 먼저 폰트를 먼저 변경해보겠습니다!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/d26ff4c4-4016-4f40-94e1-e1dd403339fd/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.30.35_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.30.35 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>font를 입력창에 입력하면 font chooser라는 옵션이 보이는데요 이 옵션을 ON해주세요!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/f2a932e2-4ba6-4cbc-b863-9e391d9f3aa8/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.31.14_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.31.14 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>저는 개인적으로 IM_Hyemin체를 좋아해서 이 font로 설정해보도록 하겠습니다!!</p>\n<p>Mac에 설치되어있는 폰트를 입력하시면 됩니다!!</p>\n<p>IM_Hyemin체 다운로드 링크</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.dgb.co.kr/cms/imhyemin/\">DGB대구은행 IM혜민체</a></p>\n<p>저는 코드는 Jetbrains Mono폰트를 좋아해서 Code는 Jetbrains Mono폰트로 설정해보도록 하겠습니다!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/f2a932e2-4ba6-4cbc-b863-9e391d9f3aa8/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.31.14_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.31.14 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>이렇게 입력을 완료하셨다면</p>\n<p>스크롤을 위로해주세요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/3457cbb5-067b-4c0a-b7c5-078b5376e4a3/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.34.41_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.34.41 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>설정을 적용하기 위해서는 앱을 재실행해야합니다!!!</p>\n<p>app relaunch라는 text를 클릭해주세요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/a2afd607-eea5-4992-9548-a6f3d9e2eb85/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.35.37_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.35.37 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>아니 이게 뭐야<del></del></p>\n<p>내가 알던 노션 맞아?? 맞냐고!!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/1827bf61-75b4-4cf8-b653-198d36127045/102_7423.jpg\" alt=\"102_7423.jpg\"></p>\n<p>놀라긴 아직 이릅니다 여러분!!</p>\n<p>이제 테마를 변경해볼건데요!!</p>\n<p>다시 <code class=\"language-text\">option + E</code> 키를 눌러주세요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/f75832fb-e0b8-4f12-a370-71a80dcac97e/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.38.22_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.38.22 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>theme을 입력해주세요!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/36a1fdfa-9ff3-4ca1-b081-83ce12bf7f89/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.38.39_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.38.39 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>이제 이곳에 뜨는 것들이 테마인데요!!</p>\n<p>드라큘라 테마로 한번 설정해보도록 하겠습니다!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/321044c2-1f09-4378-9fe4-6aa06b0a77c1/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.39.35_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.39.35 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>설정을 해준뒤에는 앱을 재실행해줘야하?!</p>\n<p>위로 스크롤을 해주세요!! (<del>트랙패드 좋아</del>)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/be9d6670-4ffb-412a-908f-239b90793369/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.40.42_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.40.42 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>아 참, 코드 폰트를 확인해봐야곘네요!! 코드도 폰트가 바뀌었나볼까요?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/2ac72b12-857c-4b66-a480-55d2991c8dfd/Screen_Shot_2021-10-05_at_1.42.43_AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-10-05 at 1.42.43 AM.png\"></p>\n<p>코드 폰트도 설정한 Jetbrains Mono 폰트와 테마에 맞게 잘 변경되었네요~!!</p>\n<p>위와 같은 방법으로 이제 나머지 설정은 여러분의 취향에 맞게 변경하시면 됩니다!!!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/secure.notion-static.com/c9ea3c5a-2773-42d3-a583-2c485a0cec26/39bfc051c9de1e3a71c5210755e4edf7.gif\" alt=\"39bfc051c9de1e3a71c5210755e4edf7.gif\"></p>\n<p>입맛에 맞게 설정해 모자랐던 2퍼센트 함께 채워보아요😊</p>\n<p>이제 칙칙한 노션은 안녕👋 👋 👋</p>\n<p>다음에 또 유용한 툴을 가지고 돌아오도록 하겠습니다!!</p>\n<p>다들 즐거운 한주 보내세요 :)</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Notion 글꼴바꾸기","date":"October 05, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Tools/notion-글꼴바꾸기/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Swift/2021-09-01-swift-class,-struct는-어디에-저장될까/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Swift에서 Class, Struct는 어디에 저장될까?","category":"Swift","draft":false}},"next":null}}}